"### Constraints\n"
"\n"
"| Constraint type           | Argument "
"type                                                                                                         "
"| "
"Description                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                             "
"|\n"
"|---------------------------|-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|\n"
